    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "Era Aviation\nFlying at its best.\nSummer Timetable\nEffective May 13, 1991\nAnnouncing New Service To Barrow\n7\nAlaska Airlines\nCOMMUTER SERVICE\nAnchorage Barrow\nHomer\nKenai Kodiak Valdez\nIliamna",
      "Quick and convenient\nconnections to Alaska's most\npopular destinations.\nBARROW\nFAIRBANKS\nANCHORAGE\nVALDEZ\nILIAMNA (\nKODIAK\nFrom Barrow to Kodiak, Valdez to Iliamna, and\n17 Western Alaskan Villages in the Kuskokwim\nDelta, Era Aviation now flies you to more Alaskan\ndestinations than ever before. For schedule infor-\nmation and reservations call your local travel agent,\nAlaska Airlines or Era Aviation.\nEra Aviation\nFlying at its best.\nAlaska Atrlines\nMILEAGE PLAN"
    ],
